Package: clash
Title: Access the Clash of Clans API
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Christopher T.", "Kenny", 
    email = "christopherkenny@fas.harvard.edu", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"), 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9386-6860")))
Description: 
    Interfaces with the official API for Clash of Clans <https://developer.clashofclans.com/#/>.
    Provides tools to work with players, clans, wars, raids, and other game events. All outputs are provided in a tidy format, where each player, clan, or attack is an observation.
